description: The suspects were located following the hack of a Europe-wide phone system.
title: Six arrested after 'Dutch torture chambers' found
title_page: Six arrested after 'Dutch torture chambers' found - BBC News
maintext: After locating the containers in April in Wouwse Plantage, near the Belgian border, police put the area under observation and found that multiple men were working on them almost every day. When the containers were almost finished, investigators decided to intervene.
